quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  37,1,"'uqsim allah taealaa bialmalayikat tasif fi ebadtha sfwfana mtrast, wbalmlaykt tzjr alsahab wtswqh bi'amr allh, wbalmlaykt tatlu dhikr allah wklamh teala. 'iina mebwdkm -ayha alnas- lawahid la sharik lh, fakhlsu lah alebadt waltae. wyqsm allah bima sha' min khlqh, 'amaa almkhlwq fala yajuz lah alqism 'iilaa ballh, falhlf bighayr allah shrk"
  37,2,"aqsm allah taealaa bialmalayikat tasif fi ebadtha sfwfana mtrast, wbalmlaykt tzjr alsahab wtswqh bi'amr allh, wbalmlaykt tatlu dhikr allah wklamh teala. 'iina mebwdkm -ayha alnas- lawahid la sharik lh, fakhlsu lah alebadt waltae. wyqsm allah bima sha' min khlqh, 'amaa almkhlwq fala yajuz lah alqism 'iilaa ballh, falhlf bighayr allah shrk"
  37,3,"aqsm allah taealaa bialmalayikat tasif fi ebadtha sfwfana mtrast, wbalmlaykt tzjr alsahab wtswqh bi'amr allh, wbalmlaykt tatlu dhikr allah wklamh teala. 'iina mebwdkm -ayha alnas- lawahid la sharik lh, fakhlsu lah alebadt waltae. wyqsm allah bima sha' min khlqh, 'amaa almkhlwq fala yajuz lah alqism 'iilaa ballh, falhlf bighayr allah shrk"
  37,4,"aqsm allah taealaa bialmalayikat tasif fi ebadtha sfwfana mtrast, wbalmlaykt tzjr alsahab wtswqh bi'amr allh, wbalmlaykt tatlu dhikr allah wklamh teala. 'iina mebwdkm -ayha alnas- lawahid la sharik lh, fakhlsu lah alebadt waltae. wyqsm allah bima sha' min khlqh, 'amaa almkhlwq fala yajuz lah alqism 'iilaa ballh, falhlf bighayr allah shrk"
  37,5,"hw khaliq alsmwat wal'ard wama bynhma, wmdbbir alshams fi mtaleha wmgharbha"
  37,6,'inna zynna alsama' aldunya bizinat hi alnjwm
  37,7,whfzna alsama' bialnujum min kuli shaytan mtmrrid eat rjym
  37,8,"la tastatie alshayatin 'ana tasil 'iilaa almala alaela, wahi alsmwat wman fiha min almlaykt, ftstme 'iilayhim 'iidha tklmu bima ywhyh allah taealaa min shreh wqdrh, wyurjamwn balshhb min kuli jht; trdana lahum ean alastmae, walahum fi aldaar alakhirat eadhab dayim mwje"
  37,9,"la tastatie alshayatin 'ana tasil 'iilaa almala alaela, wahi alsmwat wman fiha min almlaykt, ftstme 'iilayhim 'iidha tklmu bima ywhyh allah taealaa min shreh wqdrh, wyurjamwn balshhb min kuli jht; trdana lahum ean alastmae, walahum fi aldaar alakhirat eadhab dayim mwje"
  37,10,"'ila man aikhtataf min alshayatin alkhtft, wahi alkalimat yasmaeha min alsama' bsret, fylqyha 'iilaa aldhy thth, wylqyha alakhar 'iilaa aldhy thth, frbma 'adrakah alshhab almudi' qabl 'an ylqyha, warubama 'alqaha bqadar allah taealaa qabl 'an yatih alshhab, fyhrqh fayadhhab biha alakhar 'iilaa alkhnt, fykdhbwn maeaha miayat kdhbt"
  37,11,"fasal -ayha alrswl- mnkry albaeth 'ahum 'ashadu khlqana 'am man khalaqna min hadhih almkhlwqat? 'iinaa khalaqna 'abahum adam min tin lzj, yltsq baedah bbed"
  37,12,"bl ejbt -ayha alrswl- min tkdhybhm w'inkarhm albeth, waejb min 'inkarhm wa'ablagh 'anahum yastahziuwn bk, wayaskharun min qwlk"
  37,13,w'idha dhkkiru bima nasuh 'aw ghafalu eanh la yntfewn bhdha aldhikr wala ytdbbarwn
  37,14,w'idha ra'awa mejzt dallat ealaa nbwwatk yskhrwn minha wyejbwn
  37,15,"wqalu: ma hdha aldhy jit bih 'iilaa sihr zahir byin. 'a'iidha mitna wsirna trabana wezamana bialyt 'a'iinaa lamabeuthun min qbwrna ahya', 'aw yubeth abawuna aladhin mdu min qblna?"
  37,16,"wqalu: ma hdha aldhy jit bih 'iilaa sihr zahir byin. 'a'iidha mitna wsirna trabana wezamana bialyt 'a'iinaa lamabeuthun min qbwrna ahya', 'aw yubeth abawuna aladhin mdu min qblna?"
  37,17,"wqalu: ma hdha aldhy jit bih 'iilaa sihr zahir byin. 'a'iidha mitna wsirna trabana wezamana bialyt 'a'iinaa lamabeuthun min qbwrna ahya', 'aw yubeth abawuna aladhin mdu min qblna?"
  37,18,"ql lahum -ayha alrswl-: nem sawf tubethwn, wa'antum adhla' saghrwn"
  37,19,"f'inma hi nafkhat wahdt, fa'iidha hum qayimun min qbwrhm yanzurun ahwal yawm alqyamt"
  37,20,"wqalu: ya hlakna hdha yawm alhisab waljza'"
  37,21,"fyqal lhm: hdha yawm alqada' bayn alkhalq bialeadl aladhi kuntum tukadhibun bih fi aldunya wtnkrwnh"